➜Activity themed "clean air for blue skies" kicked off in N China's Hebei
http://www.sohu.com/a/417277743_162758	32538
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/ff750f634a034b6388142f73b3bba846.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Photo taken on Sep. 4 shows "clean air for blue skies" activity kicked off in Handan City, north China's Hebei Province. As a greeting to the International Day of Clean Air for blue skies on Sep. 7, the co-organized activity by the dependent office of Handan Municipal Ecology and Environment Bureau in Fengfeng District and Chunguang Primary School provides students with an opportunity to take part in environmental monitoring and learn basic knowledge of environmental protection, calling for low-carbon lifestyle. (Hao Qunying/Guangming Picture)</p>
